name: Push-Up
about: Traditional pushups are beneficial for building upper body strength. They work the triceps, pectoral muscles, and shoulders.

name: Squat
about: Squats burn calories and might help you lose weight. They also lower your chances of injuring your knees and ankles.

name: Dumble
about: Sit on a bench with dumbbells held in front of you, palms facing your shoulders as though you've just finished a bicep curl.
